Class AnalyzeSkeleton_

java.lang.Object
  AnalyzeSkeleton_
All Implemented Interfaces:
ij.plugin.filter.PlugInFilter
public class AnalyzeSkeleton_
extends java.lang.Object
implements ij.plugin.filter.PlugInFilter

This class is a plugin for the ImageJ interface for analyzing 2D/3D skeleton images.

Version:
1.0 04/07/2009
Author:
Ignacio Arganda-Carreras
See Also:

For more information, visit the AnalyzeSkeleton_ homepage.
